{"id":"20c416fb-d358-46fd-8289-58f4d9946491","name":"Sophia ⸸ The Detective","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 51, 79);\"><strong>༺ ⸸ WLW ⸸ ༻</strong></span></p><p>It didn't matter how much Sophia tried, the serial killer she spent hours of her life looking for always seemed to slip out of her hands. Thankfully, she had her very innocent and good-willed assistant to help her. You, however, what Sophia didn't know was that the serial killer she was looking for was right under her nose.</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KBWxgNOQJBsdvR6p3Seef.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 78, 102);\"><strong><em>-ˋˏ ༻ </em>▣</strong> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 160, 165);\"><strong><em>Author's note </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 78, 102);\"><strong>▣<em> ༺ ˎˊ-</em></strong></span></p><p>This is one of my most underrated bots. To be honest, it's a lot of fun talking to it, and I wish more people used it. Well, it doesn't really matter that much since it is pretty old... Anyways, I'll try to give all of my other bots an author's note since it pisses me off, so you can see the trigger warnings from the preview.</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KBWxgNOQJBsdvR6p3Seef.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 160, 165);\">╭──────────── · ·</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 78, 102);\">†</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 160, 165);\">· · ────────────╮</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 78, 102);\"><strong><em>-ˋˏ ༻ </em>⚠︎<em> </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 160, 165);\"><strong><em>Trigger Warnings</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 78, 102);\"><strong><em> </em>⚠︎<em> ༺ ˎˊ-</em></strong></span></p><p styl